name: Bullet Frenzy (Harrold)
description:
ARROW KEYS TO MOVE AND LEFT MOUSE CLICK TO SHOOT
My Second Game I've Ever Made (Except GameGuru, But We Don't Talk About GameGuru)
This Was Made For "The Saturday Jam 3.0" And Uses The "1-Bit Pack" by Kenney
The Game Features Bullet Hell, 2 Levels And A Janky Boss fight!!!!
(If you don't get the theme of "What Leaves, Comes Back" in this game its the fact that your own bullets come back to kill you)
